Company Profile

	Tronox Limited is a global leader in the mining, production and marketing of inorganic minerals and chemicals. The company operates two vertically integrated businesses: Titanium dioxide (TiO2) and Alkali Chemicals. Our company is committed to maximizing value for its shareholders, and our investor relations team works to put our financial performance into perspective.






